General.Name: Black Canyon Ltd
General.Description: Black Canyon Limited, together with its subsidiaries, focuses on mineral exploration activities in Australia. The company explores for manganese, copper, and cobalt targets. Its flagship project includes Flanagan Bore Project located in the Pilbara region of Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Subiaco, Australia.
